io.smint.clapi.consumer.integration.core.factory

Interface ISmintIoSyncFactory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SmintIoSyncFactoryFromDI

    public interface ISmintIoSyncFactory
    A factory that will create all necessary instances, necessary for the synchronization jobs.

    This factory is used by SmintIoSynchronization to drive the setup of the synchronization job. So SmintIoSynchronization is responsible for creating such a factory. Hence it will hand over the instance of ISyncTargetFactory as provided by the consumer of the library.
